# See https://help.github.com/articles/ignoring-files/ for more about ignoring files.

# Dependencies (any workspace)
**/node_modules
.pnp
.pnp.*
.yarn/*
!.yarn/patches
!.yarn/plugins
!.yarn/releases
!.yarn/versions

# Build / cache output (any workspace)
**/.next/
**/out/
**/build/
**/dist/
**/.turbo/
**/coverage/
**/.cache/

# Prisma generated client (regenerated per environment)
**/prisma/generated/

# Python
**/__pycache__/
**/*.pyc
**/.venv/
**/.pytest_cache/
**/.mypy_cache/
**/.ruff_cache/
**/*.egg-info/

# Local databases / runtime artefacts
**/*.sqlite
**/*.sqlite3
**/*.db
**/runtime/

# Compiled bootstrap artefacts (generated, never commit)
**/compiled-bootstraps/

# Env / secrets (opt-in by removing the leading bang on a specific file)
.env
.env.local
.env.*.local
**/.env
**/.env.local
**/.env.*.local
!.env.example

# Vercel
.vercel

# TypeScript
*.tsbuildinfo
next-env.d.ts

# Local data / leads (do not commit real inquiries)
data/
!data/.gitkeep

# Misc
.DS_Store
*.pem
npm-debug.log*
yarn-debug.log*
yarn-error.log*
.pnpm-debug.log*

# Editor
.idea/

